<p align="justify">This Privacy Policy, together with the Terms of service posted on our Website, set forth the general rules and policies governing your use of our Website. Depending on your activities when visiting our Website, you may be required to agree to additional terms of service.</p>
<h4>Website Visitors</h4>
<p align="justify">Like most website operators, Sahaayak collects non-personally-identifying information of the sort that web browsers and servers typically make available, such as the browser type, language preference, referring site, and the date and time of each visitor request.Sahaayak's purpose in collecting non-personally identifying information is to better understand how Sahaayak's visitors use its website. From time to time, Sahaayak may release non-personally-identifying information in the aggregate, e.g., by publishing a report on trends in the usage of its website.</p>
<p align="justify">Sahaayak also collects potentially personally-identifying information like Internet Protocol (IP) addresses for logged in users and for users leaving comments on http://sahaayakdemo.herokuapp.com blog posts. Sahaayak only discloses logged in user and commenter IP addresses under the same circumstances that it uses and discloses personally-identifying information as described below.</p>

<h4>Gathering of Personally-Identifying Information</h4>
<p align="justify">Certain visitors to Sahaayak's websites choose to interact with Sahaayak in ways that require Sahaayak to gather personally-identifying information. The amount and type of information that Sahaayak gathers depends on the nature of the interaction. For example, we ask visitors who sign up for a blog at http://sahaayakdemo.herokuapp.com to provide a username and email address.</p>

<h4>Security</h4>
<p align="justify">The security of your Personal Information is important to us, but remember that no method of transmission over the Internet, or method of electronic storage is 100% secure. While we strive to use commercially acceptable means to protect your Personal Information, we cannot guarantee its absolute security.</p>

